COMMENTS ON ANY OTHER CONDITIONS AFFECTING THIS STREAM
Not a good return of chums, but better than the rest of the local-area - possibly because of consistent water flow. The final number was probably higher than
recorded, but I was unable to get to this system for a final walk towards the end of October.
